      <h2>Marketing priorities for food and beverage brands</h2>
      <p>Food and beverage brands break when email treats every subscriber the same. The pressure point is repeat purchase windows, subscriptions, and limited-time flavors. A disciplined email marketing program must coordinate consent, lifecycle timing, product context, and margin-aware measurement — not blast more coupons.</p>
